description: Returns the  XssMatchSet that is specified by XssMatchSetId.

parameters.name: XssMatchSetId
parameters.description: The XssMatchSetId of the  XssMatchSet that you want to get. XssMatchSetId is returned by  CreateXssMatchSet and by  ListXssMatchSets.

nested_items.name: XssMatchSet
nested_items.description: Information about the  XssMatchSet that you specified in the GetXssMatchSet request. For more information, see the following topics:
XssMatchSet: Contains Name, XssMatchSetId, and an array of XssMatchTuple objects.
XssMatchTuple: Each XssMatchTuple object contains FieldToMatch and TextTransformation.
